data.description: Wonderful 2 bedroom unit with recent exterior refresh located in the 55 & older "Belfair Condominiums." Secure building with no pets & no smoking! Carpeted living room with slider to balcony. Large primary bedroom with large walk-in closet. Second bedroom with doors that open to the living room would also make a great den/office. All appliances stay including newer washer & dryer. Assigned covered parking and storage. Community room with kitchenette can be reserved for your Bingo night or whatever other fun activities you plan. Plenty of guest parking & car wash station. Low monthly dues ($311) include water, sewer, garbage & common area maintenance.
